# Stages 6 + 9 conformance harness — pinned upstream versions.
#
# Edit this file to bump. ADR-S001 §4 documents the policy:
# pin by commit SHA, never `latest`, never a branch.
#
# When the OGC org adopts the ETS into `opengeospatial/ets-ogcapi-connectedsystems10`
# and publishes a registry image, replace ETS_GIT_URL + ETS_COMMIT with
# ETS_IMAGE (e.g. `ETS_IMAGE=ghcr.io/opengeospatial/ets-ogcapi-connectedsystems10:1.0`)
# and update `conformance/run.sh` to docker pull instead of docker build.

# The Botts CS API ETS — built into TeamEngine 5.6.1 by its own multi-stage
# Dockerfile. As of 2026-05-16, no tagged release exists; the latest commit
# on `main` is the only available pin.
ETS_GIT_URL=https://github.com/Botts-Innovative-Research/ets-ogcapi-connectedsystems10.git
ETS_COMMIT=d9caf33fcd0c4a3c1a582e8ba9b12b753277afd4
ETS_COMMIT_DATE=2026-05-13
ETS_VERSION=0.1-SNAPSHOT
ETS_CODE=ogcapi-connectedsystems10

# TeamEngine version bundled by the ETS Dockerfile above. Informational —
# bumping this here does nothing unless the Botts repo is also bumped.
TEAMENGINE_VERSION=5.6.1

# TeamEngine REST defaults (Tomcat manager + ETS suite invocation).
TE_USER=ogctest
TE_PASS=ogctest

# Stage 9 — semstreams framework backend. Powers `graph.mutation.*` +
# `graph.query.*` + `graph.index.query.*` + `graph.spatial.query.*` so
# cs-api-server's NATS request/reply calls have responders. Built from
# the framework's own multi-stage docker/Dockerfile (production target).
#
# PIN POLICY: match the Go module pin in semconnect's go.mod
# (`github.com/c360studio/semstreams v1.0.0-beta.87`) so the wire
# protocol the gateway compiles against and the binary the backend
# runs share a tag. Bump the module first, conformance pin second.
SEMSTREAMS_GIT_URL=https://github.com/C360Studio/semstreams.git
# Commit SHA (not tag-object SHA). `git rev-parse HEAD` returns the
# commit a ref points at, so ensure_semstreams_vendor's idempotency
# check needs the commit SHA, not the annotated-tag object's SHA —
# otherwise every subsequent run re-clones.
SEMSTREAMS_COMMIT=38d7c5d25b6bbe9ff2d1a56c60822dc6053bad24
SEMSTREAMS_COMMIT_DATE=2026-05-29
SEMSTREAMS_VERSION=v1.0.0-beta.87
